Download FAQs

Is the app free?

Yes! FlashFusion apps are free to download and use. Premium features require a subscription.

How do I install the desktop app?

Download the installer for your OS, run it, and follow the on-screen instructions. Installation takes less than 2 minutes.

Can I use the same account on multiple devices?

Absolutely! Sign in with your FlashFusion account on any device and your projects will sync automatically.

Are my projects stored locally or in the cloud?

Both! Projects are stored in the cloud for sync across devices, with local caching for offline access.

How do I update the app?

Desktop apps auto-update when you restart. Mobile apps update through the App Store or Play Store.
